SUMMARY:Sunshine in the East (Strathmore)
DESCRIPTION:Our Sunshine in the East programs are Sunshine Centres’ newest programs! Funded by the Ontario Trillium Foundation\, join us 2 times weekly in East York to fill your mornings with fun games\, activities\, and even more sunshine! This program is exclusively for residents of 145 Strathmore Blvd.
URL:https://sunshinecentres.com/calendar/sunshine-in-the-east-3/
LOCATION:145 Strathmore Blvd\, 1st Floor Rec Room\, 145 Strathmore Blvd\, Toronto\, Ontario\, M4J 4Y9\, Canada
CATEGORIES:In-Person Programs
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://sunshinecentres.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/145-Strathmore-Blvd.jpg
END:VEVENT
