LAST-MODIFIED:20240312T153536Z
UID:145-1693821600-1693832400@sunshinecentres.com
SUMMARY:252 Sackville St. Seniors Together: A Place for All
DESCRIPTION:Our program at 252 Sackville Street began as a program for Bengali seniors living in the Regent Park community\, but it quickly grew to include a diverse group of vibrant seniors living in the area. Join us every week for arts and crafts\, gentle exercise\, fun and games\, guest speakers\, and friendly conversation as you get to know your community. This program is only for seniors residing in Regent Park.
URL:https://sunshinecentres.com/calendar/252-sackville-st-seniors-together-a-place-for-all/
LOCATION:252 Sackville street\, 7th floor recreation room\, 252 Sackville street\, 7th floor recreation room\, Toronto\, Ontario\, M5A 3E9\, Canada
CATEGORIES:In-Person Programs
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://sunshinecentres.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/252-Sackville.jpg
END:VEVENT
