SUMMARY:Mondays @ 460 Jarvis
DESCRIPTION:Open now to all seniors within the community! Held in a spacious recreational room with large windows\, a patio\, and a fantastic view of the city\, our program at 460 Jarvis brings people together. During Mondays @ 460 Jarvis\, participants meet to connect with other seniors while relaxing with laughter yoga\, getting active with light fitness\, expressing their artistic side with creative projects\, and learning something new from guest speakers.
URL:https://sunshinecentres.com/calendar/rainbow-bridges/
LOCATION:460 Jarvis St\, 4th Floor Rec Room\, 460 Jarvis St\, Toronto\, Ontario\, M4Y 2X8\, Canada
