SUMMARY:Rainbow Circle
DESCRIPTION:At our Rainbow programs\, our 2SLGBTQIA+ seniors groups\, you are likely to find engaging conversation\, arts and crafts\, and educational workshops. These programs are a safe and inclusive space where our 2SLGBTQIA+ seniors can connect\, share experiences\, and build meaningful relationships while enjoying activities such as games and trivia\, light exercise\, and outings into the community.
URL:https://sunshinecentres.com/calendar/rainbow-circle/
LOCATION:460 Jarvis St\, 4th Floor Rec Room\, 460 Jarvis St\, Toronto\, Ontario\, M4Y 2X8\, Canada
CATEGORIES:In-Person Programs
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://sunshinecentres.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/460-Wellesley-Jarvis-Place.jpg
END:VEVENT
