UID:164-1693994400-1694005200@sunshinecentres.com
SUMMARY:St. James Town Programming (Wellesley Community Centre)
DESCRIPTION:Our Wellesley Community Centre and Carlton Street locations are a breath of fresh air for St. James Town seniors. Every week\, seniors keep active and connected as they catch up with one another over refreshments\, release stress during breathing and mediation sessions\, express their creative side with art projects\, and learn something new from fun and informative workshops.
URL:https://sunshinecentres.com/calendar/st-james-town-programming/
LOCATION:Wellesley Community Centre\, 495 Sherbourne St\, Toronto\, Ontario\, M4X 1L1\, Canada
CATEGORIES:In-Person Programs
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://sunshinecentres.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Wellesley-Community-Centre.jpg
END:VEVENT
