LAST-MODIFIED:20250128T164614Z
UID:191-1694008800-1694012400@sunshinecentres.com
SUMMARY:Main Program: Short Story Book Club!
DESCRIPTION:The Sunshine Short Story Club is a peer-led gathering of friendly 55+ seniors. We meet to read and discuss public-domain and free-to-read stories\, ranging from classic tales to modern science fiction.  Sometimes we listen to audio short story presentations. See our current and upcoming stories on our website: https://eldertalk.ca/
URL:https://sunshinecentres.com/calendar/main-program-short-story-book-club/
CATEGORIES:Virtual Programs
END:VEVENT
