SUMMARY:Sunshine @ Davenport
DESCRIPTION:When the seniors living at 250 Davenport Road requested one of our programs in their building\, we happily obliged. Now every Friday\, 250 Davenport Road is a hub of camaraderie and warmth as seniors gather together and enjoy light exercise\, arts and crafts\, games and trivia\, and other activities.
URL:https://sunshinecentres.com/calendar/sunshine-davenport/
